      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "…………\nそれ、かわりに私が出ます。出たいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……\nI'll take her place. I want to do it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.8000126521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 206.1569997787
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "確かその番組収録の日、オフをもらってましたけど\nお休み返上してでも、私、出たいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know I had that day off‚\nbut even if it means giving up my break‚ I want to do it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.8609392863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに仕事詰めになるけど、大丈夫か？\nさくらの場合、病気の影響で食事制限もあるし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It'll definitely be packed with work‚ but are you okay?\nIn Sakura's case‚ you also have dietary restrictions due to your illness…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.7333459854,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 222.9368865013
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です！　むしろ今はお仕事頑張りたくて\nウズウズしてるぐらいですし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm fine! Rather‚ I'm itching to work hard right now‚\nI'm so eager!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.5666793187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 229.9368865013
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
