      "text": "食事制限も、スイーツがメインなら、チーズとか\nドライフルーツとか使ってない限りは大丈夫です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As for dietary restrictions‚ if it's mainly sweets‚\nas long as they don't use cheese or dried fruits‚ I'll be fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.9333459854,
      "sfxList": []
